-- Turkey's Halkbank says to study banking opportunities in Serbia
-- By Ece Toksabay
-- Tue Jun 03, 2014 11:04AM EDT
-- None



ISTANBUL, June 3 (Reuters) - Turkish state-controlled lender Halkbank <HALKB.IS> said on Tuesday it had been given permission by regulators in Serbia to research the country's banking system with a view to potentially entering the market in the future.

